text: Five little caterpillars jumping in the mud..
One fell off and bumped his head
Mamma called the doctor and the doctor said
No more caterpillars jumping on the mud!
Four little caterpillars jumping in the mud..
One fell off and bumped his head
Mamma called the doctor and the doctor said
No more caterpillars jumping on the mud!
Three little caterpillars jumping in the mud..
One fell off and bumped his head
Mamma called the doctor and the doctor said
No more caterpillars jumping on the mud!
Two little caterpillars jumping in the mud..
One fell off and bumped his head
Mamma called the doctor and the doctor said
No more caterpillars jumping on the mud
One little caterpillars jumping in the mud.
One fell off and bumped his head
Mamma called the doctor and the doctor said
Put those caterpillars right to bed
